&lt;p&gt;ICONIQ Studio is dedicated to thoughtfully cultivating our remarkable community of the world’s brightest minds. As the firm’s creative, strategic, and operational center for network engagement, we are structured around three pillars: Communications &amp;amp; Content, Events &amp;amp; Experiences, and Network Intelligence &amp;amp; Engagement. In close collaboration with teams across the firm, we connect people and ideas by producing uncommon content, meaningful insights, and extraordinary experiences to deepen our relationships and amplify our impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze existing datasets to map and assess ICONIQ’s global network, providing insights to inform strategies for community engagement and growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with leadership and cross-functional teams across the firm in harnessing the power of our collective network, identifying opportunities for strategic introductions and connections, invitations to unique events, and pinpointing levers for community expansion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with internal technology team to help build and manage our Salesforce customization projects and identify/implement other relevant systems, while maintaining data integrity and best practices for scalability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and deliver presentations and reports that highlight network status, success stories, and value creation ensuring transparency and alignment across teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and maintain detailed documentation of network processes, data flow, and project requirements to streamline future initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ideal Candidate Background:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of relevant industry experience and a Bachelor’s degree with a strong academic background, with demonstrated entrepreneurial mindset.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience building systems that integrate and synthesize data from various sources to surface actionable insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent project management skills and proven ability to multitask in a fast-moving environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong integrity, confidence, emotional intelligence, and ability to diplomatically navigate complex situations, lead diverse stakeholders, and drive execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient in using Outlook, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Google Suite, Salesforce, Tableau, and Monday.com.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deeply curious and thoughtful, experience and/or interest in understanding how Artificial Intelligence and beyond, will play a role for data mapping initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Offer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comprehensive Medical, Dental and Vision Insurance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Life and disability insurance coverage as well as family and wellness benefits including mental health benefits, fertility benefits, and back-up childcare.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A matching 401(k) program.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commuter Benefits program.&lt;/li&gt;
